programme.desc: James Kroll hunts Texas brush country with his Smith & Wesson Performance Center handgun; Mike Clerkin heads to Missouri with his bow; and Dr. Deer explores how the moon phase affects the rut(n)

programme.title: Adrenaline
programme.desc: As the rut is winding down throughout the Midwest, Iowa crew members Bill Jackson and Cordell Turner refuse to throw in the towel. The deer season marathon has most bowhunters hanging it up, but this crew's persistence pays off on an Iowa brute(n)

programme.title: The Western Hunter
programme.desc: Chris Denham hunts Sitka blacktail deer on Kodiak Island for the first time while Nate makes a return visit after an incredible trip the prior year(n)

programme.title: West of Texas
programme.desc: Stephen is guiding his dad in Mexico on a trophy mule deer hunt. After a tough week of hunting, they make a last-ditch effort on a wide Mexico giant(n)

programme.title: Winchester Deadly Passion
programme.desc: After putting in for 10-years, Melissa Bachman finally draws a rifle mule deer tag on the Kaibab in Arizona. This is a sought after tag and it doesn't take long before the big bucks start showing themselves(n)

programme.title: Hardcore Pursuit
programme.desc: Celebrate 10 Years of HCP with the crew. They'll sit back and take a good look at 10 years of making HARDCORE Pursuit. It's been a wild ride and the boys look forward to many more great seasons of HCP(n)

programme.title: Full Draw Adventures
programme.desc: Bill and the crew reflect back on some of the lessons learned from the season and highlight some unseen footage from the year(n)

programme.title: Sheep Shape
programme.desc: Chad Hall and friends keep pursuing Dall sheep, moose and caribou in the Northwest Territories(n)

programme.title: Major League Bowhunter
programme.desc: Part 1. Matt and Chipper fulfill a lifelong dream of hunting elk with archery equipment. With free range of the NRA Whittington Center in northeast New Mexico, Duff and Chipper have high hopes of closing the distance on a giant bull elk(n)

programme.title: Bowhunter TV
programme.desc: Curt Wells heads for his favorite Kansas deer haunt and runs smack into lockdown, but he's got a plan to beat it. In Moment of Truth, Curt talks about keeping your presence unknown(n)

programme.title: Trained Assassins
programme.desc: Cragg Fitz continues his quest chasing whitetails in Nebraska with Terry. Slade Priest will be hunting his property in Mississippi, while Blake heads back to Illinois to try to fill his muzzleloader tag(n)

programme.title: In-Fisherman
programme.desc: It's right up the staff's alley to cut through any complications on the way to fine fishing. They use live bait for snook; slip into two-timing mode to do battle with crappies, perch and largemouths on ice; and reveal spoon secrets for smallmouths(n)

programme.title: The Gypsy Angler
programme.desc: Captain Ray Van Horn heads to Louisiana for large predatory fish in the pogey schools(n)

programme.title: North American Whitetail Television
programme.desc: James Kroll hunts Texas brush country with his Smith & Wesson Performance Center handgun; Mike Clerkin heads to Missouri with his bow; and Dr. Deer explores how the moon phase affects the rut(n)

programme.title: Whitetail Fix

programme.title: Whitetail Explorer

programme.title: Dominant Bucks
programme.desc: The prostaff demonstrates tips and tactics for utilizing staging areas and ambush points for mature whitetails(n)

programme.title: Respect the Game TV
programme.desc: The Solid Decap is the star. RTG members take the Solid Decap to the turkey woods(n)

programme.title: Big Deer TV
programme.sub-title: Best and Worst of Big Deer
programme.desc: Few good days and many tough ones add up to another fun and interesting season for Mike and friends(n)

programme.title: GunVenture
programme.desc: A behind-the-scenes look at The Reliant, and a first-hand look at how guns were incorporated from start to finish. Also: Chris Cerino dispels common movie and TV myths, and Ryan heads to a gun-training school for actors and stunt people(n)

programme.title: Guns & Gear
programme.desc: Introducing Caracal's Enhanced F polymer pistol and its many features. Also: Springfield Armory's 1911 RO line, Ruger's 10/22 TD integrally-suppressed barrel, more Shields from Smith & Wesson and new Barnes Bullets VOR-TX and Precision Match ammo(n)

programme.title: Jon Baker's Guide 4 Adventure
programme.desc: After surviving a 400 ft fall during a mountain goat hunt, Jon brings his new outlook on life to the forefront(n)

programme.title: Predator Nation
programme.desc: Making coyotes run(n)

programme.title: Trailing the Hunter's Moon
programme.desc: Larry Weishuhn and Blake Barnett highlight the best of their 2016 hunts from throughout the world(n)

programme.title: Trijicon's World of Sports Afield

programme.title: Hornady's Dark & Dangerous
programme.sub-title: Big Bulls by Land and Sea

programme.title: Petersen's Hunting Adventures

programme.title: Savage Outdoors
programme.desc: Mike Stroff and Jamie Satterfield are heading to the Brooks range to hunt caribou, grizzly bear and Dall sheep. This hunt is the adventure of a lifetime and they get to do it together. It is rare the guys get to do a hunt of this caliber together(n)

programme.title: Buckventures' The Woodsman
